<br />

<br />
Pet summoned wepaons proccing slow, rune, stun, snare lure DD.
<br />

<br />
Turn CoTH on EVERYwhere then add code to turn it off in *specific small areas*, only a few zones need be exempt.
<br />

<br />
Make HoTE pets have 1500hp each or AOE immune, how bloody hard is that to do?
<br />

<br />
Flag mobs as summoned and elemental, make anti-summoned spells affect them, so most golems, all elementals, pets and a few other creatures are affected by these.
<br />

<br />
Make Fire pet cast Lure of Fire and root self at a specific time interval so it has best Dps of any pet but cna't tank for crap. Or make it melee pet weak melee pathetic hit points but procs FLames of Ro (400hp lure)
<br />

<br />
If pet is aggro it breaks invis, and make invis not kill pet, solves that problem right off.
<br />

<br />
All pet heals should be 3 sec cast for all classes, no one has itme to mess aorund with slow heals.
